      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring the variable valve timing operates within factory tolerances. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a factory-spec suspension geometry that preserves its telepathic handling. A purist\u2019s spec, ready for the apex.",
